Air Products and Chemicals, Inc. 7201 Hamilton Boulevard Allentown, PA 18195-1501
Access the Q1 earnings teleconference scheduled for 11:00 a.m. Eastern Time (ET) on January 26 by calling (719) 457-2633 and entering passcode 354933, or listen on the Web:
