Execution Copy
This ASSET PURCHASE AGREEMENT is made as of March 31, 2006 (this "Agreement"), by and between Air Products and Chemicals, Inc., a Delaware corporation ("Seller"), and BASF Corporation, a Delaware corporation ("Buyer"). Certain other terms are used herein as defined below in or elsewhere in this Agreement.
Section 1
This Agreement sets forth the terms and conditions upon which Buyer is purchasing the Purchased Assets (defined below) and assuming the Assumed Liabilities (defined below) from Seller, and Seller is selling the Purchased Assets and transferring the Assumed Liabilities to Buyer.
NOW, THEREFORE, the Parties, intending to be legally bound hereby, for good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are hereby acknowledged, and in consideration of the mutual covenants contained herein, hereby agree as follows:
