3. .
Closing
3.1 . The closing for the Transactions (the "Closing") shall be held at the offices of BASF Corporation at 10:00 a.m. (local time) on the date hereof, unless the Parties agree in writing to another date or place. The date on which the Closing occurs is referred to herein as the "Closing Date." The Closing shall be effective as of 11:59 pm., EST, on the Closing Date.
