Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
On October 25, 2006, the company issued a press release announcing its earnings for the fourth quarter of fiscal year 2006. A copy of the press release is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Form 8-K. The press release, including all financial statements, is furnished and is not deemed to be filed.
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits.
