Air Products and Chemicals, Inc. 7201 Hamilton Boulevard Allentown, PA 18195-1501
Access the Q1 earnings teleconference scheduled for 10:00 a.m. Eastern Time on January 21 by calling (719) 325-4810 and entering passcode 1645128, or listen on the
